author: ajsutton
content:
For the record, the notification you got came from a spam message which tagged `@` everyone. The `@` mod message was to notify the mods about the spam - they did their job and banned the spammer including deleting all their posts.  Sadly discord doesn't reset notifications when a message is deleted so you all just wound up seeing the message to the mods and not the original one that actually caused the notifications.

You can disable mass notifications by right clicking on the server, notifications and checking the option to suppress them.
